The paper introduces a new algorithm that combines the benefits of contrastive learning with the power of deep generative models. The algorithm is designed to identify and enhance salient latent features in a target dataset compared to some background. This makes it likely that the paper belongs to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
